interface IDoor {
 + State: DoorState
 + Open()
 + Close()
}

enum DoorState {

 Closed
}

class SimpleDoor {

 + Close()
}

interface ISmartDoorFeature {

 + EnableAlert()

}

class Notify {

 + EnableAutoClose()
 + NotifyAndClose()

class Timer {
 + Start()
 + SetTimer(int interval)
 + EnableAlert()
 + EnableAutoClose()
 + NotifyAndClose()
}

class SmartDoor {
 - features: List<ISmartDoorFeature>
 + Features: List<ISmartDoorFeature>

}
